OL,3,C#68.6 million Whitesands flood defence
OL,4,Cproject approved
OL,6,FThe #68.6 million Whitesands flood
OL,7,Fdefence project has been approved by
OL,8,FDumfries and Galloway Council.
OL,10,FThe decision was made at a full
OL,11,Fcouncil meeting on Thursday afternoon
OL,12,Fand will see #54.9 million of Scottish
OL,13,FGovernment funding unlocked and
OL,14,Fconstruction is now set to begin in
OL,15,FSpring 2026.
OL,17,FThe council say that the project is a
OL,18,F"key initiative to safeguard Dumfries
OL,19,Ffrom the River Nith flooding while
OL,20,Frevitalising the riverside area."
