OL,3,C#68.6 million Whitesands flood defence
OL,4,Cproject approved
OL,6,FThe funding will create a new
OL,7,Friverside corridor at Greensands,
OL,8,FWhitesands and Dock Park which will
OL,9,Fsee new walkways, landscaping and
OL,10,Fpublic spaces.
OL,12,FFunding for the project has almost
OL,13,Fdouble from its initial estimate in
OL,14,F2023 from #37.5 million to #68.6
OL,15,Fmillion, which the council say is down
OL,16,Fto design development and inflation.
