OL,3,C#68.6 million Whitesands flood defence
OL,4,Cproject approved
OL,6,FCouncillor Katie Hagmann, Convener of
OL,7,FDumfries and Galloway Council, said:
OL,8,F"Today's decision secures essential
OL,9,Ffunding needed to protect Dumfries
OL,10,Ffrom Whitesands flooding. It's a
OL,11,Fsignificant investment in our town's
OL,12,Ffuture prosperity and resilience.
OL,14,F"By agreeing to move forward in a
OL,15,Fpositive direction with this project,
OL,16,Fwe are safeguarding the community and
OL,17,Fcreating long-term improvements to the
OL,18,FWhitesands, Greensands and Dock Park
OL,19,Fareas.
