OL,3,C#68.6 million Whitesands flood defence
OL,4,Cproject approved
OL,6,F"This flood protection project will
OL,7,Fhelp keep homes and businesses safe
OL,8,Ffrom the next major flood and it also
OL,9,Fcreates a better environment along the
OL,10,Friverside for residents and visitors
OL,11,Falike."
OL,13,FIn a statement Dumfries and Galloway
OL,14,FCouncil said: "The town has suffered
OL,15,Fregular flooding for centuries,
OL,16,Fdamaging property and deterring
OL,17,Finvestment, with risks expected to
OL,18,Fworsen under climate change.
