OL,3,C#68.6 million Whitesands flood defence
OL,4,Cproject approved
OL,6,F"The project aims to deliver a
OL,7,Fpermanent 1-in-75-year flood
OL,8,Fprotection standard ` a flood that has
OL,9,Fa 1.3% chance of happening in any
OL,10,Fgiven year ` for Dumfries,
OL,11,Fsafeguarding homes, businesses and key
OL,12,Finfrastructure.
OL,14,F"Councillors agreed to allocate #13.7
OL,15,Fmillion (20%) of the project cost,
OL,16,Fsecuring #54.9 million (80%) in match-
OL,17,Ffunding from the Scottish Government."
